    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>I would suggest to restore you tomcat to the initial install condition without changes, and then add your jars (mongo, guava, etc) to the <code>/lib</code> directory under the tomcat installation directory, as described <a href=\"http://tomcat.apache.org/tomcat-7.0-doc/class-loader-howto.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">here</a>.</p>\n\n<p>Also, it would be helpful if you post which class is missing.</p>\n"
